definitions.definition: A knife ; especially, a clasp-knife , pocket knife , or sheath knife .

main_definition: A knife ; especially, a clasp-knife , pocket knife , or sheath knife .

definitions.definition: A coarse greyish double blanket worn by countrywomen, in the west of England, over the shoulders, like a cloak or shawl.
A whittle shawl ; a kind of fine woollen shawl, originally and especially a white one.
